# Our First Pod With Kubectl run


Fiz a instalação do MikroK8s, olhar a pasta "kubernetes-local-install"

Kubectl Cheat Sheet
https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/kubectl/cheatsheet/

Kubectl for Docker Users
https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/kubectl/docker-cli-to-kubectl/



# Comandos

kubectl version
kubectl run my-nginx --image nginx
kubectl get pods  // lista os pods
kubectl get all  //  lista os services, pods e etc
kubectl delete deployment my-nginx
kubectl get all  // vai ter apenas uma linha do service






